erlang_twitter contains an Erlang twitter client. This code is still under active development.

Using this module is pretty simple:
1> inets:start().
2> twitter_client:start("myname", "pass").
3> twitter_client:call(myname, status_update, [{"status", "Testing the erlang_twitter twitter_client.erl library."}]).
4> twitter_client:call(myname, user_timeline).
